---
title: Ultimate Thai Green Style Chicken Curry with Tenderstem®, Baby Corn, Jasmine Rice and Peanuts
description: Looking for a taste of everyday luxury? This Ultimate Thai Green Style Chicken Curry is our best ever version, with premium ingredients for an extra special twist on a classic recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ultimate-thai-green-style-chicken-curry-cc509807-f39eb741.jpg
